  narrativeLines:
  - Why is it suddenly so.. eerie?
  - I just need to go home, man..
  - AHHHH :0
  - Am I in a horror game? Should I look for a flashlight?
  - Oh, shit.. a phone!!
  - I better go follow the lights
  - Finally, my sushi dinner
  - I shoud've picked my laundry earlier..
  - I better go follow the lights
  - I'll just follow the lights, this is too creepy
  - Sooo hungry. Misaki is the only place opened right now
